title: Thursday Post Show (8-26-21)
itunes:title: Thursday Post Show (8-26-21)
description:
Bobby shares his list of Top 5 New Artists right now. There’s also a woman who got 2 years in jail for lying about having COVID and coughing on food at a store. We also talked about whether to watch The White Lotus on HBO. We also dive into Amy and if someday she will go full “Eat, Pray, Love” and leave the show. Also we wonder if it’s child abuse for this 5-year-old became one of the youngest kids to hike the Appalachian Trail.
